<div id="right">
    <div class="padding">
      <h1>About us</h1>
      <p class="path"> <a href="/en/cerit-sp/">CERIT Science Park</a>
&raquo; <a href="/en/cerit-sp/About/">About us</a>
</p>
 <!-- Content -->
<div align="left">
<h2>
<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0);"><b style="font-size: 12px;"><span style="font-size: 18pt;">What is CERIT Science Park?</span></b></span></div>
<div align="left">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', serif;">A new science-technology park and a business incubator of Masaryk University (Faculty of Informatics and Institute of Computer Science) constructed within the frame of the Operational Programme Enterprise and Innovation of the Ministry of Industry and Trade. CERIT is an acronym derived from the English translation of the institution's name: <strong>C</strong>entre for <strong>E</strong>ducation, <strong>R</strong>esearch and <strong>I</strong>nnovation in IC<strong>T</strong>. </span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', serif;">CERIT Science Park is being constructed on the premises of FI and ICS MU on Botanick√° street in Brno as an <strong>independent eight-storey building </strong>within the Centre for Education, Research and Innovation in ICT &ndash; CERIT, covering a total area of ca <strong>3 700 m</strong><sup>2</sup>.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<div style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', serif;"> It is planned to come into operation in July 2014 at the latest.</span></div>
<div style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</div>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: rgb(128, 0, 0);"><b><span style="font-size: 18pt;">CERIT Science Park</span></b></span></p>
<ul>
    <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', serif;">CERIT Science park will, under preferential terms, provide <strong>premises, expert advisory services and outsourcing of selected company processes</strong> in the common interest of the the CERIT Science Park members and Masaryk University as its owner,</span></li>
    <li style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 'Palatino Linotype', serif;">it will offer <strong> the business incubator environment</strong> to starting spin-off companies.</span></li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1" class="MsoListParagraph"><span style="mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Palatino Linotype&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;
mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-bidi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-fareast-language:CS"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p align="left" class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
</h2>
